                     <interp inst="t17860222-103-off528" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17860222-103-cd529" type="crimeDate">11th day of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-103-off528 t17860222-103-cd529"></join>, one boiling copper, value 10 s. belonging to 
                     
                        <persName id="t17860222-103-victim1033" type="victimName">
