                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-103-defend1031 t17860222-103-punish533"></join>
               confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
